name: Pattern Puzzle - Sewing connections [part 1]
description:
Happy 400 followers on twitter @natived_ 
I love you one by one, experimental journey continues...

Non generated. All artworks are carefully created and unique, with a name.

They're also a piece of a puzzle you can combine with more or let it be alone.
Although, if you put few next to each other, it seems like they can communicate.
Nobody really knows how and why;
Combine the puzzle as you wish and tell your own story.
